<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Database Backup - Nepal Climate Hub</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dddddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0;">Database Backup Notification</h2>
    <p>Dear Administrator,</p>
    <p>Please find attached the automated database backup zip file for the Nepal Climate Hub CMS.</p>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
      <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <th style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eeeeee; text-align: left; width: 40%;">Project</th>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eeeeee;">Nepal Climate Hub CMS</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eeeeee; text-align: left;">Backup Date</th>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eeeeee;">{{backupDate}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <th style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eeeeee; text-align: left;">Status</th>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eeeeee; color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold;">Successful</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="color: #e74c3c; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold;">
      Important Note: Please keep this backup secure as it contains sensitive database records.
    </p>
    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 20px 0;" />
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0;">
      This is an automated system notification from Nepal Climate Hub. Please do not reply directly to this email.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
